# Docs style

- Low-energy reading: few words; tables and mermaid over prose.
- No verbose sections; one idea per bullet or row.
- Mermaid encouraged for flows and architecture.

## File roles

| File | Content |
|------|---------|
| `docs/blueprint.md` | Engine Symbols · Threads · gated Flow · maintenance → `blueprint.mdc` |
| `docs/strategies.md` | Math only |
| `docs/project.md` | Objectives + Next + Backlog only · maintenance → `project-backlog.mdc` |
| `README.md` | User use this to refer build command - Do Not Edit without explicit user permission |
| `docs/GraphTickerModel.md` | Data Structure North Star - Do Not Edit without explicit user permission |
| `docs/BinanceWsSamples.md` | Live Binance WS request/response samples - Do Not Edit without explicit user permission |
| `docs/BinanceFilters.md` | Binance spot exchangeInfo filters (LOT_SIZE, NOTIONAL, tick) - Do Not Edit without explicit user permission|

Do not mix concerns across these files.
